=== S形装饰 ===
[[File:Landau_carriage,_1816.jpg|256px]]
部分灵车尾部有S形状的装饰条，其学名为Landau Bar，来源于豪华马车（Landau）的折叠软顶，昂贵的Landau马车被设计为上层阶级的豪华马车，所以铰链机构设计成了较为美观的S形。<ref>Haajanen, Lennart W., ''Illustrated dictionary of automobile body styles,'' New York: McFarland Publishing, {{ISBN|978-0-7864-1276-1}}.</ref>

1935年的《汽车工程师协会手册》将Landau定义为“一种封闭型车身，可通过使用Landau接头来打开或折叠后四分之一”。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wuM3AAAAMAAJ&q=Landau+closed-type+body+with+provision+for+opening+or+folding+the+rear+quarter,+by+use+of+landau+joints+which+precludes+the+use+of+quarter+windows |page=730 |title=S.A.E. Handbook |publisher=Society of Automotive Engineers |year=1935 |accessdate=2014-04-03 |archive-date=2020-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725210054/https://books.google.com/books?id=wuM3AAAAMAAJ&q=Landau+closed-type+body+with+provision+for+opening+or+folding+the+rear+quarter%2C+by+use+of+landau+joints+which+precludes+the+use+of+quarter+windows |dead-url=no }}</ref>
