=== 灵柩救护两用车 ===
[[File:DFVAC_1970s_Cadillac_Miller_Meteor_color.jpg|256px]]的 凯迪拉克 Miller Meteor两用车]]
灵柩救护两用车为灵柩车式样，并安装了警示灯、对讲机、急救包、车厢内折叠座椅等设备，并可以在灵柩车与救护车之间切换，主要存在于美国。流星汽车（Meteor Motor Car）1915年在美国推出了第一个价格低廉的“组合式”灵车和救护车。<ref name="popularmechanics.com">{{cite web |title=Hearse Homecoming |url=http://www.popularmechanics.com/automotive/collector_cars/1267851.html |website=www.popularmechanics.com |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060718221620/http://www.popularmechanics.com/automotive/collector_cars/1267851.html |archivedate=2006-07-18}}</ref> 这种两用车反应出一个时代，美国的殡葬行业除了主营业务外还提供紧急救护车服务，尤其是在较小的城镇和农村地区。

这些两用车通常基于凯迪拉克商用底盘，知名的车身制造厂商有 Superior、Miller-Meteor、Hess & Eisenhardt 和 Cotner-Bevington。<ref name="car-nection.com">{{cite web |title=The (new) Cadillac Database Professional Cars on Cadillac Chassis  1967 - 1969 |url=http://www.car-nection.com/yann/dbas_txt/prof6769.htm |website=www.car-nection.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060827182135/http://www.car-nection.com/yann/dbas_txt/prof6769.htm |archivedate=2006-08-27}}</ref>其中 Meteor 汽车与 Miller 汽车陆续于1954年和1956年被 Wayne Works 收购后合并为 Miller-Meteor 并制造了 1959 凯迪拉克 Miller-Meteor。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.coachbuilt.com/bui/w/wayne/wayne2.htm|title=Wayne Works Part II, Wayne Corp., Divco-Wayne Corp., School Bus, Wayne Wheeled Vehicles, Transicoach, Dublin Foundry - Coachbult.com|website=www.coachbuilt.com|access-date=2017-08-27|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205202421/http://www.coachbuilt.com/bui/w/wayne/wayne2.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

随着汽车厂商逐渐缩小汽车底盘，以及[[紧急医疗服务|紧急医疗服务]]的推行，提高了救护车车载设备和车内空间的要求。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Emergency Medical Services: At the Crossroads|chapter=Chapter: 2 History and Current State of EMS|url=https://www.nap.edu/read/11629/chapter/4|language=en|access-date=2019-11-22|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308161150/https://www.nap.edu/read/11629/chapter/4|dead-url=no}}</ref>这类两用车逐渐被淘汰。
